  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Application Tester / QA Tester",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are seeking a detail-oriented <strong>Application Tester / QA Tester</strong> to support the development and quality assurance of mobile and web applications. The role involves testing applications for functionality, usability, and performance to ensure a smooth user experience.</p><p>Training and guidance will be provided, so prior testing experience is not mandatory.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Conduct functional and user experience testing of applications</p></li><li><p>Identify, document, and report bugs or issues accurately</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with developers and product teams to reproduce and resolve issues</p></li><li><p>Participate in the design and execution of test cases and test plans</p></li><li><p>Ensure applications meet quality and usability standards</p></li><li><p>Assist with maintaining testing documentation and logs</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Good command of English, both written and spoken</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and analytical skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with smartphones, computers, and software applications</p></li><li><p>Ability to follow instructions and work independently</p></li><li><p>Prior QA or testing experience is a plus but not required</p></li></ul>",
